        <num>47-3-100</num>
        <content>
          <p>The retirement allowance of a member shall be based on the membership service rendered or established by him since he last became a member and, if he has a prior service certificate in full force and effect, the amount of the prior service so certified.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1943, p. 640, ยง 4.)</p>
